                    <li><strong>Curl Your Fingers:</strong> Gently curl all of your fingers into your palm, making a
                        fist. Make sure your fingers are comfortably folded.</li>
                    <li><strong>Position Your Thumb:</strong> Now, focus on your thumb, which is the key to this sign.
